snippet.title: Lanota [Nintendo Switch] Overview Trailer
snippet.description:
Lanota offers a unique blend of dynamic music rhythm gameplay and storytelling, delivering a colorful narrative and enticing soundtrack in one package! Check out this overview to learn more about the game.

Out on Nintendo Switch on 14th June in North America and 20th June in Europe / Australia / New Zealand.

Follow us on Twitter! - https://twitter.com/FlyhighWorks_en
